@kek, it seems that having admins manually categorize guilds with inactive GMs isn't working that well right now. May I ask for your opinion on having a checkbox to see uncategorized guilds and having an "unfiltered all" that's different from the regular All again?

(Also, can you categorize +Ruqqie?)

<sup> - sfrohne [If you're going to post a screenshot of this comment, **don't** censor my username]</sup>

